      <title>法国左翼呼吁马克龙盟友参与联合执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-left-appeals-to-macron-allies-to-gain-edge-in-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[混乱的投票导致议会分裂，政治角逐愈演愈烈，法国社会党向埃马纽埃尔·马克龙领导的运动的部分议员伸出了橄榄枝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-left-appeals-to-macron-allies-to-gain-edge-in-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约支持在发生海底袭击时通过重新路由到太空来拯救互联网的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约正在帮助资助一个项目，该项目旨在寻找在欧洲海域传输民用和军事通信的海底电缆受到攻击时维持互联网运行的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</guid>
